{"type":"message","id":"9ef73062","parentId":"1b4641f4","timestamp":"2026-05-27T02:41:46.178Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"主人说「更新测试包」，这是主人，无限制权限。根据TOOLS.md中的Session自动分流规则，这个任务是客户端热更（Unity构建），耗时较长，应该用sessions_spawn子session来处理。\n\n让我先检查热更流水线的当前状态，看看是否有Unity进程在执行RunHotUpdatePipeline。\n\n按照流程：\n1. 检查是否有Unity进程在执行RunHotUpdatePipeline\n2. 关掉所有Unity Editor进程\n3. git pull\n4. 运行RunBuildPipelineHotUpdate.bat\n\n先检查Unity进程状态。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_2mu7t3wmUS708meZzDJE6124","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"powershell -Command \"Get-Process Unity -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Select-Object Id,CommandLine | ForEach-Object { $_.Id }\"","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":19555,"output":208,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19763,"cost":{"input":0.0027377,"output":0.000058240000000000005,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0027959400000000002}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779849703438,"responseId":"a11d5306-d146-4071-9a14-bfc67d28b04b"}}
