{"type":"message","id":"66236b7e","parentId":"c2871146","timestamp":"2026-05-27T02:41:59.286Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, no Unity process running. Now let me spawn a sub-agent to handle the entire hot update pipeline. According to TOOLS.md:\n\n1. Check no Unity running the hot update pipeline (done, none running)\n2. Kill all Unity Editor processes (none running, skip)\n3. git pull in E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\n4. Submodules handled by pipeline itself\n5. Run RunBuildPipelineHotUpdate.bat\n6. Check build result from log\n7. Notify in dev group on success, or private msg on failure\n\nLet me spawn a sub-agent for this entire workflow since it will take a while.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"主人，开始更新测试包～先检查一下 Unity 进程，然后走热更流水线。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_UdqT3ujW4yGBVlpj1Qye0783","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"task":"# 更新测试包（客户端热更流水线）\n\n## 任务背景\n主人 Yousan(叶枝君) 要求更新测试包（客户端热更）。我是 sub-agent，负责执行整个热更流水线。\n\n## 工作目录\nC:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\n\n## 执行流程\n\n### 前置检查\n- 主人 open_id: ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f（完全信任）\n- Unity 项目路径: E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv\n- Git 仓库: E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\n- 日志文件: E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv\\BuildPipeline_RunHotUpdate.log\n- 热更入口: YYZY.BuildPipeline.BuildPipeline.RunHotUpdatePipeline\n- Unity 路径: C:\\Program Files\\Unity\\Hub\\Editor\\2020.3.49f1\\Editor\\Unity.exe\n- 热更 BAT: E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv\\RunBuildPipelineHotUpdate.bat\n\n### 步骤1: 检查 Unity 进程\n先检查是否有 Unity 进程正在执行 RunHotUpdatePipeline：\n```powershell\nif (Get-Process Unity -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue) { Write-Output \"有 Unity 进程在运行\" } else { Write-Output \"无 Unity 进程\" }\n```\n如果有 Unity 在跑热更流水线，则终止任务并通知主人「已有流水线在执行，请等待完成」。\n\n### 步骤2: 关掉所有 Unity Editor 进程\n```powershell\nGet-Process Unity -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Stop-Process -Force\n```\n（步骤1已确认无Unity进程，此步可跳过）\n\n### 步骤3: git pull 更新主仓库\n```powershell\ncd E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\ngit pull\n```\n记录 git pull 结果。\n\n### 步骤4: 运行热更流水线 BAT\n直接运行（不要包 cmd/c 或 powershell）：\n```\nE:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv\\RunBuildPipelineHotUpdate.bat\n```\n这会启动 Unity 并执行热更流程（打资源 + 上传CDN），需要等待完成。\nUnity 退出后继续。\n\n### 步骤5: 检查编译结果\n扫描日志文件检查是否有错误：\n```powershell\nSelect-String -Path 'E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv\\BuildPipeline_RunHotUpdate.log' -Pattern 'error CS\\d+:|git更新失败|Build completed with'\n```\n\n**判断标准：**\n- 匹配到关键字 → 视为失败\n- 无匹配 + Unity 退出码 0 → 视为成功\n\n### 步骤6: 通知结果\n\n**成功时（开发群 @兵王）：**\n```powershell\ncd C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\nnode scripts/feishu_send_group.mjs oc_59afc01122ec0cd04ca4d8c5103c7a77 hotupdate-ok\n```\n兵王 open_id: ou_348eeddd81d4c03865f9f1684fce6966\n\n**失败时（私聊通知主人）：**\n不要发群消息。用 sessions_send 私聊通知主人结果（包括错误信息）。\n\n### 注意\n- 默认增量构建（不清除 Bundles 缓存）\n- Unity 退出码 0 不代表流水线完全成功！必须扫日志文件检查 error CS/git更新失败/Build completed with errors\n- 用 bat 直接执行，不要拼内联 PowerShell 长命令\n- 每一步执行状态变化及时反馈给主 session","mode":"run","context":"isolated","label":"hotupdate-client"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":112,"output":1079,"cacheRead":19840,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21031,"cost":{"input":0.000015680000000000002,"output":0.00030212,"cacheRead":0.00055552,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00087332}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779849708888,"responseId":"6047e0df-3b3f-4204-a9cf-17c380a269b0"}}
