commit properly.\n\nLet me fix it:\n1. Enter the submodule\n2. `git checkout YYZY_1V1_V1.0_WeekVersion_0430`\n3. `git pull`\n\nThen for the main repo:\n1. `git pull`\n\nThen run the pipeline.\n\nBut about \"不执行流水线里面的拉新\" - I think the master means the fix is: since I do all git work manually before running the pipeline, the detached HEAD issue won't happen again. The pipeline's internal Git拉新 step might still try to run, but if the submodule is on a proper branch with updated content, it should work fine.\n\nAlternatively, maybe the master wants me to modify the pipeline definition in Unity to remove the Git拉新 step. But that's a Unity Editor operation I can't do from command line.\n\nI think the intent is: before running the pipeline, do all git pull/update manually, so that the pipeline's internal Git拉新 step either doesn't need to do anything or is less likely to fail. Let me proceed.\n\nLet me fix the submodule first.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"找到问题了。服务器子模块 `Server`（即 battle1v1）在 detached HEAD 状态。它的分支是 `YYZY_1V1_V1.0_WeekVersion_0430`，我切过去再拉一下。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_fXeylCH6CF4oTohViSSk6807","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"powershell -Command \"cd E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv\\Assets\\DidaScript\\GameLogic\\Solo\\Server; git checkout YYZY_1V1_V1.0_WeekVersion_0430; git pull\"","timeout":30}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":2476,"output":889,"cacheRead":24704,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":28069,"cost":{"input":0.00034664,"output":0.00024892,"cacheRead":0.000691712,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001287272}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779853364060,"responseId":"57207abd-6949-40cd-8bdc-5d315734881d"}}
