internal context private (don't mention system/log/stats/session details or announce type).\n<<<END_OPENCLAW_INTERNAL_CONTEXT>>>"}],"timestamp":1779853768022,"provenance":{"kind":"inter_session","sourceSessionKey":"agent:main:subagent:bc07f764-a513-43d0-8828-dcc2f56a5fda","sourceChannel":"webchat","sourceTool":"subagent_announce"}}}
{"type":"message","id":"c9727acb","parentId":"dd636017","timestamp":"2026-05-27T03:49:34.397Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The retry also failed. The pipeline's internal Git拉新 step is still running and failing on the same `battle1v1` submodule. Plus there's a CDN issue.\n\nLet me analyze:\n\n1. The pipeline's internal Git拉新 step (`PullBattleModuleForce()`) still ran and failed. It seems to specifically target `battle1v1` and pulls it in a way that doesn't respect the branch checkout I did.\n\n2. CDN upload also failed (404 Not Found + not a git repository)\n\nThe key issue is that the pipeline's Git拉新 step cannot be disabled externally - it's part of the Unity BuildPipeline configuration. The master said \"不执行流水线里面的拉新\" - meaning the Git拉新 step should be removed/disabled from the pipeline configuration itself.\n\nThis would require opening the Unity Editor's BuildPipeline window and removing/modifying the Git拉新 step. Since I can't do that via CLI, I need to inform the master of the situation and ask them to either:\n1. Disable/remove the Git拉新 step in the BuildPipeline window\n2. Or configure the submodule properly\n\nAdditionally, there's the CDN 404 error which is another issue.\n\nLet me report this to the master.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"主人，第二次重跑又失败了 😓\n\n这次虽然有进步（HybridCLR、Lua编译、AB打包都过了），但还是有两个问题：\n\n### ❌ 问题1：流水线内 Git拉新 还在跑\n我虽然手动修好了子模块，但流水线内部的 `PullBattleModuleForce()` 依然在拉 `battle1v1` 子模块，又报了 `git更新失败`。这个步骤需要在 Unity Editor 的 BuildPipeline 窗口里手动去掉/禁用——我这边命令行搞不定。\n\n### ❌ 问题2：CDN 上传也出错了\n- `fatal: not a git repository` — CDN 仓库检测失败\n- `404 Not Found` — 下载/上传 CDN 文件失败\n- `获取Server.json模板文件失败` — EditorConfig 配置缺失\n\n### 需要你帮忙的两件事：\n1. **打开 Unity BuildPipeline 窗口**，把「Git拉新」/ `PullBattleModuleForce` 这个步骤删掉或禁用\n2. **检查 CDN 相关配置** — EditorConfig 里的 ServerConfigTemplate / CDN Git 仓库路径是否正确\n\n都改好之后跟我说一声，我再跑一次～"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":35260,"output":520,"cacheRead":1920,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37700,"cost":{"input":0.0049364000000000005,"output":0.00014560000000000002,"cacheRead":0.00005376,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0051357600000000005}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779853768026,"responseId":"768adc4d-075e-4d0a-9088-e82cc438c6df"}}
