{"type":"message","id":"b8dd7381","parentId":"f503d956","timestamp":"2026-05-27T04:09:38.265Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can tell the master exactly what the data says:\n\n1. **GitPull (\"Git拉新\")** at offset 45365 → **❌ OFF** (`00 00 00 00 00`) — 已取消勾选 ✅\n2. **PipelineCheck** (\"打包检查和准备\") — 大部分渠道都是 ON，少数 OFF\n3. **PipelineBuild** (\"打包\") — 大部分渠道 ON\n4. **PipelineUndoChange** (\"回退\") — 所有渠道都是 OFF\n5. **HybridCLRSet** (\"HybridCLR设置\") — ON\n6. **ExecuteMenuForceResolve** (\"Google特殊操作\") — ON\n\nSo GitPull IS disabled in the config file as the master said. Time to re-run the pipeline!\n\nLet me also check the CDN-related config to see if there's anything wrong there. The previous failure also had CDN 404 issues.\n\nLet me look at the \"热更\" (HotUpdate) pipeline configuration more carefully. The PipelineHotUpdate entry doesn't have the checkbox pattern - it starts with `08 00 5a 00` which suggests it might be a string parameter step rather than a toggle step.\n\nWait actually - PipelineHotUpdate appears to be a **method** step, not a step name within a pipeline. The steps are listed by their method names. Let me look at what steps are actually in the 热更 pipeline.\n\nHmm, this is getting complex. Let me just report to the master what I found - GitPull is confirmed OFF - and ask if I should re-run the pipeline now.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"主人，`BuildPipelineConfig.bytes` 读取完毕，确认 **Git拉新（GitPull）已经是 ❌ OFF（取消勾选）状态**了 ✅\n\n几个关键步骤的状态：\n\n| 步骤 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| **Git拉新（GitPull）** | ❌ OFF |\n| 打包检查和准备（PipelineCheck） | ✅ ON（热更渠道） |\n| 打包（PipelineBuild） | ✅ ON（热更渠道） |\n| HybridCLR设置 | ✅ ON |\n| 回退 | ❌ OFF（所有渠道） |\n\n现在 Git 拉新已经不会再跑了。要我重新跑一次热更流水线吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1852,"output":479,"cacheRead":72320,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":74651,"cost":{"input":0.00025928,"output":0.00013412,"cacheRead":0.002