{"type":"message","id":"411b26c5","parentId":"e4c49c95","timestamp":"2026-05-27T05:08:21.604Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"主人让我重跑热更流水线。GitPull 已经取消勾选了，直接 spawn sub-agent 跑吧。\n\n在跑之前，先确认一下：\n1. GitPull 已取消勾选 ✅\n2. 子模块 battle1v1（Server）已修好 ✅\n3. 主仓库已 git pull ✅\n\n直接 spawn 子 session 跑流水线。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"收到，直接开跑～"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_drPjarhcQohtOh9bzQiS3394","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"label":"hotupdate-client-v3","mode":"run","context":"isolated","task":"# 重跑热更流水线（第三次尝试 - GitPull已禁用）\n\n## 背景\n主人已经取消了流水线内「Git拉新」步骤的勾选，并且之前这些也已经处理好：\n- ✅ battle1v1(Server)子模块已切回分支 YYZY_1V1_V1.0_WeekVersion_0430\n- ✅ 主仓库 git pull 已更新\n- ✅ 其他子模块正常\n- ✅ GitPull 已从配置文件取消勾选\n\n## 执行\n\n### 步骤1: 运行热更 BAT\n直接执行（不要包 cmd/c 或 powershell）：\n```\nE:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv\\RunBuildPipelineHotUpdate.bat\n```\n等待 Unity 进程完成后继续。\n\n### 步骤2: 检查编译结果\n```powershell\nSelect-String -Path 'E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv\\BuildPipeline_RunHotUpdate.log' -Pattern 'error CS\\d+:|git更新失败|Build completed with'\n```\n\n**判定：**\n- 匹配到关键字 → ❌ 失败\n- 无匹配 + Unity 退出码 0 → ✅ 成功\n\n### 步骤3: 通知\n**成功 → 开发群 @兵王：**\n```\ncd C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\nnode scripts/feishu_send_group.mjs oc_59afc01122ec0cd04ca4d8c5103c7a77 hotupdate-ok\n```\n\n**失败 → 私聊通知主人，不发群消息。**\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":35394,"output":534,"cacheRead":32768,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":68696,"cost":{"input":0.00495516,"output":0.00014952000000000002,"cacheRead":0.000917504,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.006022184}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779858495596,"responseId":"eb547eb7-2e14-4696-8f82-89ef0cd5472e"}}
