{"type":"message","id":"8b999174","parentId":"e1f93296","timestamp":"2026-05-27T05:13:15.216Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK, so `IsBuildActionValid` checks `BuildAction is { IsLoad: true }`. It's about whether the build action (the method reference) is loaded/valid, not about whether it's checked/unchecked.\n\nThe \"Selected\" property is what determines if a step is checked in the UI. Let me look at the config to see the Step class definition.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_8jTFS9698D9AxNp1egbp2498","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv\\Assets\\Editor\\BuildPipeline\\BuildPipelineConfig.cs"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":489,"output":146,"cacheRead":73344,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":73979,"cost":{"input":0.00006846,"output":0.00004088,"cacheRead":0.002053632,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002162972}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779858793051,"responseId":"62e62457-68c6-4a3d-9775-e4ea1ddcd961"}}
{"type":"message","id":"768d8ff8","parentId":"8b999174","timestamp":"2026-05-27T05:13:15.224Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_8jTFS9698D9AxNp1egbp2498","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"﻿using System.Collections.Generic;\nusing System;\nusing System.Linq;\nusing UnityEngine;\nusing Object = UnityEngine.Object;\n\nnamespace YYZY.BuildPipeline\n{\n    public class BuildPipelineStep : ISerializable, ICloneable\n    {\n        public StaticMethod BuildAction = new StaticMethod();\n        public bool Selected { set; get; }\n        public string Name { set; get; }\n\n        public BuildPipelineStep()\n        {\n            BuildAction = new StaticMethod();\n            this.Selected = true;\n        }\n\n        public bool IsBuildActionValid => BuildAction is { IsLoad: true };\n\n        public void Deserialize(ISerializeReader s)\n        {\n            s.Read(ref BuildAction);\n            Selected = s.ReadBoolean();\n            Name = s.ReadString();\n        }\n\n        public void Serialize(ISerializeWriter s)\n        {\n            s.Write(BuildAction);\n            s.Write(this.Selected);\n            s.Write(this.Name);\n        }\n\n        public object Clone()\n        {\n            var ret = new BuildPipelineStep();\n            ret.Selected = this.Selected;\n            ret.Name = this.Name;\n            ret.BuildAction = this.BuildAction.Clone() as StaticMethod;\n            return ret;\n        }\n    }\n\n    public class BuildPipelineLine : ISerializable, ICloneable\n    {\n        //自定义名称\n        public string Name;\n        public string group;\n        public bool hasShortcut;\n        public List<BuildPipelineStep> Steps { private set; get; }\n\n        public BuildPipelineLine()\n        {\n            Name = \"\";\n            group = \"默认\";\n            hasShortcut = false;\n            Steps = new List<BuildPipelineStep>();\n        }\n\n        public BuildPipelineLine(string name, string group)\n        {\n            Name = name;\n            this.group = group;\n            hasShortcut = false;\n            Steps = new List<BuildPipelineStep>();\n        }\n\n        public void Deserialize(ISerializeReader s)\n        {\n            Name = s.ReadString();\n            Steps = s.Read<List<BuildPipelineStep>>();\n            group = s.ReadString();\n            hasShortcut = s.ReadBoolean();\n        }\n\n        public void Serialize(ISerializeWriter s)\n        {\n            s.Write(Name);\n            s.Write(Steps);\n            s.Write(group);\n            s.Write(hasShortcut);\n        }\n\n        public object Clone()\n        {\n            var ret = new BuildPipelineLine\n            {\n                Name = Name,\n                group = group,\n                hasShortcut = false\n            };\n            foreach (var step in this.Steps)\n            {\n                ret.Steps.Add(step.Clone() as BuildPipelineStep);\n            }\n\n            return ret;\n        }\n        \n        public void CloneStep(int index)\n        {\n            var step = Steps[index];\n            Steps.Add(step.Clone() as BuildPipelineStep);\n        }\n\n        public void Swap(int index_a, int index_b)\n        {\n            if (Steps != null && index_a != index_b && index_a >= 0 && index_a < Steps.Count && index_b >= 0 &&\n                index_b < Steps.Count)\n            {\n                (Steps[index_a], Steps[index_b]) = (Steps[index_b], Steps[index_a]);\n            }\n        }\n\n        public void CheckAll()\n        {\n            foreach (var step in Steps)\n            {\n                step.Selected = true;\n            }\n        }\n    }\n\n    public class BuildPipelineConfig : ISerializable\n    {\n        public const int APIConfigVersion = 4;\n        public const string PipelineName = \"新建流水线\";\n\n        public List<BuildPipelineLine> BuildLines { get; private set; }\n\n        public BuildPipelineLine SettingLine { get; private set; }\n\n        public List<BuildPipelineStep> ExecuteStack { set; get; }\n\n        private List<string> groupList;\n\n        public List<string> GroupList\n        {\n            get { return groupList ??= GetAllLineByGroup().Keys.ToList(); }\n            set => groupList = value;\n        }\n\n        public bool IsExecuteFinished\n        {\n            get { return ExecuteStack == null || ExecuteStack.Count == 0; }\n        }\n\n        public bool Exists(string name)\n        {\n            return GetPipeLine(name) != null;\n        }\n\n        public BuildPipelineLine GetPipeLine(string name)\n        {\n            foreach (var p in BuildLines)\n            {\n                if (p.Name == name)\n                {\n                    return p;\n                }\n            }\n\n            return null;\n        }\n\n        public BuildPipelineConfig()\n        {\n            BuildLines = new List<BuildPipelineLine>();\n            SettingLine = new BuildPipelineLine();\n            SettingLine.Name = PipelineName;\n            ExecuteStack = new List<BuildPipelineStep>();\n        }\n\n        public BuildPipelineLine ClonePipeline(BuildPipelineLine pipline)\n        {\n            var l = pipline.Clone() as BuildPipelineLine;\n            BuildLines.Add(l);\n            return l;\n        }\n\n        public Dictionary<string, List<BuildPipelineLine>> GetAllLineByGroup()\n        {\n            var res = new Dictionary<string, List<BuildPipelineLine>>();\n            foreach (var line in BuildLines)\n            {\n                if (res.TryGetValue(line.group, out var list))\n                {\n                    list.Add(line);\n                }\n                else\n                {\n                    list = new List<BuildPipelineLine>()\n                    {\n                        line,\n                    };\n                    res.Add(line.group, list);\n                }\n            }\n\n            return res;\n        }\n\n        public string AddGroup()\n        {\n            string templeteName = \"NewGroup\";\n            string newGroupName = templeteName;\n            int count = 1;\n            while (GroupList.Contains(newGroupName))\n            {\n                newGroupName = templeteName + \"_\" + count;\n                count++;\n            }\n\n            GroupList.Add(newGroupName);\n            return newGroupName;\n        }\n\n        public void RenameGroup(string newName, string oldName)\n        {\n            var index = groupList.IndexOf(oldName);\n            groupList[index] = newName;\n            foreach (var line in BuildLines)\n            {\n                if (line.group == oldName) line.group = newName;\n            }\n        }\n        \n        public bool RemoveGroup(string group)\n        {\n            var dic = GetAllLineByGroup();\n            if (dic.TryGetValue(group, out var list))\n            {\n                if (list.Count > 0) return false;\n                groupList.Remove(group);\n                return true;\n            }\n            else\n            {\n                groupList.Remove(group);\n                return true;\n            }\n        }\n\n        public string GetNewPipelineName()\n        {\n            string templeteName = \"NewPipeline\";\n            string newPipelineName = templeteName;\n            int count = 1;\n            while (BuildLines.Find((p) => p.Name == newPipelineName) != null)\n            {\n                newPipelineName = templeteName + \"_\" + count;\n                count++;\n            }\n\n            return newPipelineName;\n        }\n        \n\n        public void AddBuildPipeline(BuildPipelineLine pipeline)\n        {\n            BuildLines.Add(pipeline);\n        }\n\n        public void RemoveLine(int index)\n        {\n            if (index > 0 && index < BuildLines.Count)\n            {\n                BuildLines.RemoveAt(index);\n            }\n        }\n\n        public void Deserialize(ISerializeReader s)\n        {\n            BuildLines = s.Read<List<BuildPipelineLine>>();\n\n            SettingLine = s.Read<BuildPipelineLine>();\n            SettingLine.Name = PipelineName;\n            if (s.Version >= APIConfigVersion)\n            {\n                ExecuteStack = s.Read<List<BuildPipelineStep>>();\n            }\n\n            GroupList = s.Read<List<string>>();\n        }\n\n        public void Serialize(ISerializeWriter s)\n        {\n            s.Write(BuildLines.ToArray());\n            s.Write(SettingLine);\n            s.Write(ExecuteStack);\n            s.Write(GroupList.ToArray());\n        }\n    }\n}"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1779858795224}}
{"type":"message","id":"7908cd8f","parentId":"768d8ff8","timestamp":"2026-05-27T05:13:25.520Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the data format better!\n\nThe `BuildPipelineStep` has:\n- `BuildAction` (StaticMethod) - the method reference\n- `Selected` (bool) - whether it's checked in the UI\n- `Name` (string) - the display name\n\nThe serialization order in `Serialize()`:\n1. `s.Write(BuildAction)` - the method reference\n2. `s.Write(this.Selected)` - boolean (checked/unchecked)\n3. `s.Write(this.Name)` - display name\n\nNow looking at the binary data for GitPull:\n```\n07 00 47 69 74 50 75 6c 6c 00 00 00 00 00 09 00 47 69 74 e6 8b 89 e6 96 b0\n```\n\nThe `BuildAction` is a `StaticMethod` serialized as well. Let me look at how `StaticMethod` is serialized to understand the full structure better.\n\nBut wait - the serialization order is: `BuildAction`, `Selected` (bool), `Name` (string).\n\nAfter \"GitPull\" (7 bytes), the next 5 bytes are `00 00 00 00 00`. But `Selected` is `s.ReadBoolean()` which would be 1 byte (0x00 or 0x01). But there are 5 zero bytes.\n\nLet me look at StaticMethod serialization to understand what comes between the name and the boolean.\n\nActually, maybe the StaticMethod serialization includes the method name as part of it, and the \"GitPull\" string is already inside the StaticMethod. Then the Selected boolean follows, then the Name.\n\nWait, looking at it differently:\n- `07 00` = string length 7\n- `47 69 74 50 75 6c 6c` = \"GitPull\" (this is the method name inside BuildAction/StaticMethod)\n- Then StaticMethod might serialize more data after the method name\n- Then Selected = boolean (1 byte)\n- Then Name string: `09 00 47 69 74 e6 8b 89 e6 96 b0` = \"Git拉新\" (length 9)\n\nSo the 5 zero bytes `00 00 00 00 00` include:\n1. The rest of StaticMethod's serialization (4 bytes?)\n2. Selected boolean = 0x00 (the 5th byte)\n\nHmm, but if Selected is the 5th byte and it's `00`, that means it's unchecked. But earlier in my analysis I was looking at `00 00 00 00 00` as 5 bytes, and the last byte being `01` for checked steps.\n\nWait, looking at the PipelineCheck step:\n```\n0d 00 50 69 70 65 6c 69 6e 65 43 68 65 63 6b 00 00 00 00 00 15 00\n```\n- `0d 00` = length 13\n- \"PipelineCheck\" (name of StaticMethod)\n- `00 00 00 00 00` = StaticMethod extra data (4 bytes) + Selected(false) (1 byte)\n- `15 00` = length 21\n- `e6 89 93 e5 8c 85 e6 a3 80 e6 9f a5 e5 92 8c e5 87 86 e5 a4 87` = \"打包检查和准备\" (display name)\n\nAnd checked PipelineCheck:\n```\n0d 00 50 69 70 65 6c 69 6e 65 43 68 65 63 6b 00 00 00 00 01 15 00\n```\nSame but the 5th byte is `01` = Selected(true)\n\nSo the structure is:\n1. Method name (length-prefixed string)\n2. 4 bytes of StaticMethod extra data (always `00 00 00 00` for method-only StaticMethods)\n3. 1 byte for Selected boolean\n4. Display name (length-prefixed string)\n\nFor GitPull:\n```\n07 00 47 69 74 50 75 6c 6c 00 00 00 00 00 09 00\n```\n- `07 00` = length 7\n- \"GitPull\" = method name\n- `00 00 00 00 00` = 4 extra bytes + Selected = FALSE (unchecked)\n\nSo GitPull IS unchecked (`Selected = false`) in the config bytes! But it's still being executed...\n\nLet me check the ExecuteStack and ExecutePipeline logic to see why.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_MOrpqNF14ywgY4s30k9k1362","name":"read","arguments":{"offset":100,"path":"E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv\\Assets\\Editor\\BuildPipeline\\BuildPipeline.cs","limit":130}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1755,"output":1114,"cacheRead":73856,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":76725,"cost":{"input":0.0002457,"output":0.00031192000000000004,"cacheRead":0.002067968,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002625588}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779858795225,"responseId":"dd4cf04d-b48b-4ddf-8418-51d305a87420"}}
{"type":"message","id":"f6cdf574","parentId":"7908cd8f","timestamp":"2026-05-27T05:13:25.528Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_MOrpqNF14ywgY4s30k9k1362","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n        /// <summary>\n        /// 无参入口，供 bat：<c>-executeMethod YYZY.BuildPipeline.BuildPipeline.RunHotUpdatePipeline</c>。\n        /// 执行名为 <see cref=\"HotUpdatePipelineName\"/> 的流水线中的<strong>全部有效步骤</strong>（与编辑器里整条线执行一致，非仅勾选步骤）。\n        /// </summary>\n        public static void RunHotUpdatePipeline()\n        {\n            if (!IsCommandLineBatchMode())\n            {\n                Execute(HotUpdatePipelineName);\n                return;\n            }\n\n            Debug.Log($\"BuildPipeline.RunHotUpdatePipeline (batch, all steps): '{HotUpdatePipelineName}'\");\n            BeginBatchCli(HotUpdatePipelineName, selectedOnly: false);\n        }\n\n        private static bool IsCommandLineBatchMode()\n        {\n            return Array.IndexOf(Environment.GetCommandLineArgs(), \"-batchmode\") >= 0;\n        }\n\n        private static void BeginBatchCli(string pipeline, bool selectedOnly)\n        {\n            if (string.IsNullOrEmpty(pipeline))\n            {\n                Debug.LogError(\"BuildPipeline CLI: pipeline name is empty.\");\n                EditorApplication.Exit(1);\n                return;\n            }\n\n            EditorPrefs.SetBool(BatchExitAfterDonePrefKey, true);\n            var mode = selectedOnly ? \"Selected\" : \"Full\";\n            Debug.Log($\"BuildPipeline CLI (batch) mode={mode} pipeline='{pipeline}'\");\n\n            var pipe = Config.GetPipeLine(pipeline);\n            if (pipe == null)\n            {\n                Debug.LogError(\"pipeline \" + pipeline + \" not found!\");\n                ClearBatchExitRequest();\n                EditorApplication.Exit(1);\n                return;\n            }\n\n            try\n            {\n                Config.ExecuteStack.Clear();\n                ExecutePipeline(pipe, selectedOnly);\n            }\n            catch (Exception e)\n            {\n                Debug.LogException(e);\n                ClearBatchExitRequest();\n                EditorApplication.Exit(1);\n                return;\n            }\n\n            TryBatchExitNowIfDone();\n        }\n\n        private static void ClearBatchExitRequest()\n        {\n            EditorPrefs.SetBool(BatchExitAfterDonePrefKey, false);\n        }\n\n        private static void TryBatchExitNowIfDone()\n        {\n            if (!EditorPrefs.GetBool(BatchExitAfterDonePrefKey, false))\n                return;\n            if (!IsDone())\n                return;\n\n            ClearBatchExitRequest();\n            var code = LastRunSucceeded ? 0 : 1;\n            if (code != 0)\n                Debug.LogError(\"Build pipeline finished with errors or was canceled.\");\n            EditorApplication.Exit(code);\n        }\n\n        public static void ExecuteSelected(string pipeline)\n        {\n            var pipe = Config.GetPipeLine(pipeline);\n            if (pipe != null)\n            {\n                Config.ExecuteStack.Clear();\n                ExecutePipeline(pipe, true);\n            }\n            else\n            {\n                Debug.Log(\"pipeline \" + pipeline + \" not found!\");\n            }\n        }\n\n        public static void SaveConfig()\n        {\n            if (config != null)\n            {\n                var path = ConfigFilePath;\n                using (var w = serializer.CreateWriter(File.OpenWrite(path)))\n                {\n                    w.Version = BuildPipelineConfig.APIConfigVersion;\n                    w.Write(BuildPipelineConfig.APIConfigVersion);\n                    w.Write(config);\n                }\n                AssetDatabase.Refresh();\n            }\n        }\n\n        public static void ClearConfig()\n        {\n            config = null;\n        }\n\n        internal static void ExecuteContinued()\n        {\n            SetExecuteState(ExecuteState.Executing);\n            while (!Config.IsExecuteFinished)\n            {\n                if (EditorApplication.isCompiling)\n                {\n                    SaveConfig();\n                    SetExecuteState(ExecuteState.Suspend);\n                    Debug.Log(\"-----Jump out the build step-----\");\n                    return;\n                }\n\n                var lastIndex = Config.ExecuteStack.Count - 1;\n                var step = Config.ExecuteStack[lastIndex];\n                Config.ExecuteStack.RemoveAt(lastIndex);\n                if (step != null)\n\n[87 more lines in file. Use offset=230 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1779858805527}}
