{"type":"message","id":"feaf62bb","parentId":"498d10da","timestamp":"2026-05-27T05:13:31.318Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_Oyc9xJWfX9yWYb3QlUOB2587","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        private static void ExecutePipeline(BuildPipelineLine line, bool selectedOnly)\n        {\n            if (line != null)\n            {\n                if (Config.ExecuteStack.Count > 0)\n                {\n                    Config.ExecuteStack.RemoveAt(Config.ExecuteStack.Count - 1);\n                }\n\n                //嵌套执行\n                for (int i = line.Steps.Count - 1; i >= 0; --i)\n                {\n                    var step = line.Steps[i];\n                    if (step.IsBuildActionValid && (!selectedOnly || step.Selected))\n                    {\n                        Config.ExecuteStack.Add(step);\n                    }\n                }\n                ExecuteContinued();\n            }\n\n[10 more lines in file. Use offset=307 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1779858811318}}
{"type":"message","id":"63ba25d6","parentId":"feaf62bb","timestamp":"2026-05-27T05:13:38.933Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Found the issue!\n\nLine 299: `if (step.IsBuildActionValid && (!selectedOnly || step.Selected))`\n\nWhen `selectedOnly = false` (which is the case for batch mode - `BeginBatchCli(HotUpdatePipelineName, selectedOnly: false)`), the condition becomes:\n`step.IsBuildActionValid && (!false || step.Selected)` = `step.IsBuildActionValid && (true || step.Selected)` = `step.IsBuildActionValid`\n\nSo when `selectedOnly = false`, ALL valid steps are executed regardless of their `Selected` flag!\n\nThe comment at line 103-106 even says:\n```\n/// 执行名为 <see cref=\"HotUpdatePipelineName\"/> 的流水线中的<strong>全部有效步骤</strong>（与编辑器里整条线执行一致，非仅勾选步骤）。\n```\n\nIt literally says \"all valid steps\", not \"only selected steps\".\n\nSo the issue is that the batch mode (`RunHotUpdatePipeline`) is called with `selectedOnly: false`, which means ALL steps with valid build actions are executed, regardless of their Selected checkbox state.\n\nFor the GitPull step, `IsBuildActionValid` returns true because the method reference is loaded, so even though `Selected` is false, the step still runs.\n\nThe fix would be:\n1. Change `selectedOnly: false` to `selectedOnly: true` in the `RunHotUpdatePipeline` method\n2. Or directly disable the step in code\n\nBut I can't modify the Unity source code and rebuild without the user's permission. Let me report this to the master.\n\nActually wait - the master already knows about the pipeline and unchecked the GitPull step. The issue is that the pipeline code explicitly runs all steps regardless of the checkbox in batch mode. Let me tell the master about this finding.\n\nActually, the master said \"不执行流水线里面的拉新, 以后自己使用git命令更新主工程\" - so he wants me to handle git updates myself and skip the pipeline's git pull. But the pipeline code forces all steps to run in batch mode.\n\nThe solution would be either:\n1. Change `selectedOnly: false` to `selectedOnly: true` in `BuildPipeline.cs:147`\n2. Or comment out the GitPull step entirely in the code\n3. Or modify the `GitPull()` method to check the config and skip\n\nLet me tell the master what I found and ask if he wants me to fix the code.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"主人，找到根本原因了！\n\n这是 `BuildPipeline.cs` 里 `RunHotUpdatePipeline` 的代码：\n\n```csharp\n// 执行名为 \"热更\" 的流水线中的全部有效步骤\n// （与编辑器里整条线执行一致，非仅勾选步骤）\nBeginBatchCli(HotUpdatePipelineName, selectedOnly: false);\n```\n\n注意 `selectedOnly: false` 👈\n\n再看 `ExecutePipeline` 里的判断逻辑：\n\n```csharp\nif (step.IsBuildActionValid && (!selectedOnly || step.Selected))\n```\n\n当 `selectedOnly = false` 时，条件变成：\n```\nstep.IsBuildActionValid && (true || step.Selected)\n```\n→ 只看 `IsBuildActionValid`，**完全不管 Selected 勾没勾**！\n\n所以你在编辑器里取消勾选的 GitPull，在命令行跑整条流水线时**被强制执行了**，因为这个方法设计就是「跑全部有效步骤，不管勾选」。\n\n要修的话，把 `RunHotUpdatePipeline()` 里的 `selectedOnly: false` 改成 `selectedOnly: true` 就行，要我改吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":268,"output":752,"cacheRead":78080,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":79100,"cost":{"input":0.00003752,"output":0.00021056000000000002,"cacheRead":0.00218624,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00243432}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779858811319,"responseId":"fff30a3f-d6d5-4c9d-a810-7fcc9c3a4abe"}}
