{"type":"message","id":"bcfb7268","parentId":"783d5683","timestamp":"2026-05-27T06:08:48.580Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"主人让我改代码。需要修改 `BuildPipeline.cs` 中的 `RunHotUpdatePipeline()` 方法，把 `selectedOnly: false` 改为 `selectedOnly: true`。\n\nLet me first read the exact code to find the precise text to change.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_VbqN3yI0aWYL7DgcRXEf3984","name":"read","arguments":{"offset":100,"path":"E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv\\Assets\\Editor\\BuildPipeline\\BuildPipeline.cs","limit":55}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":14111,"output":154,"cacheRead":65536,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":79801,"cost":{"input":0.00197554,"output":0.00004312,"cacheRead":0.001835008,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0038536679999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779862126025,"responseId":"8da9a8e3-779e-4c79-8c92-2cd7f0e4137d"}}
{"type":"message","id":"95a41d6f","parentId":"bcfb7268","timestamp":"2026-05-27T06:08:48.694Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_VbqN3yI0aWYL7DgcRXEf3984","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n        /// <summary>\n        /// 无参入口，供 bat：<c>-executeMethod YYZY.BuildPipeline.BuildPipeline.RunHotUpdatePipeline</c>。\n        /// 执行名为 <see cref=\"HotUpdatePipelineName\"/> 的流水线中的<strong>全部有效步骤</strong>（与编辑器里整条线执行一致，非仅勾选步骤）。\n        /// </summary>\n        public static void RunHotUpdatePipeline()\n        {\n            if (!IsCommandLineBatchMode())\n            {\n                Execute(HotUpdatePipelineName);\n                return;\n            }\n\n            Debug.Log($\"BuildPipeline.RunHotUpdatePipeline (batch, all steps): '{HotUpdatePipelineName}'\");\n            BeginBatchCli(HotUpdatePipelineName, selectedOnly: false);\n        }\n\n        private static bool IsCommandLineBatchMode()\n        {\n            return Array.IndexOf(Environment.GetCommandLineArgs(), \"-batchmode\") >= 0;\n        }\n\n        private static void BeginBatchCli(string pipeline, bool selectedOnly)\n        {\n            if (string.IsNullOrEmpty(pipeline))\n            {\n                Debug.LogError(\"BuildPipeline CLI: pipeline name is empty.\");\n                EditorApplication.Exit(1);\n                return;\n            }\n\n            EditorPrefs.SetBool(BatchExitAfterDonePrefKey, true);\n            var mode = selectedOnly ? \"Selected\" : \"Full\";\n            Debug.Log($\"BuildPipeline CLI (batch) mode={mode} pipeline='{pipeline}'\");\n\n            var pipe = Config.GetPipeLine(pipeline);\n            if (pipe == null)\n            {\n                Debug.LogError(\"pipeline \" + pipeline + \" not found!\");\n                ClearBatchExitRequest();\n                EditorApplication.Exit(1);\n                return;\n            }\n\n            try\n            {\n                Config.ExecuteStack.Clear();\n                ExecutePipeline(pipe, selectedOnly);\n            }\n            catch (Exception e)\n            {\n                Debug.LogException(e);\n                ClearBatchExitRequest();\n                EditorApplication.Exit(1);\n                return;\n\n[162 more lines in file. Use offset=155 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1779862128694}}
{"type":"message","id":"02e84199","parentId":"95a41d6f","timestamp":"2026-05-27T06:08:53.044Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need to modify:\n1. The comment that says \"全部有效步骤\" → \"仅勾选步骤\"\n2. The Debug.Log message\n3. The `selectedOnly: false` → `selectedOnly: true`\n\nLet me make the edit.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_awZvNqEduFVpFyyweN5f6312","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv\\Assets\\Editor\\BuildPipeline\\BuildPipeline.cs","edits":[{"oldText":"        /// <summary>\n        /// 无参入口，供 bat：<c>-executeMethod YYZY.BuildPipeline.BuildPipeline.RunHotUpdatePipeline</c>。\n        /// 执行名为 <see cref=\"HotUpdatePipelineName\"/> 的流水线中的<strong>全部有效步骤</strong>（与编辑器里整条线执行一致，非仅勾选步骤）。\n        /// </summary>\n        public static void RunHotUpdatePipeline()\n        {\n            if (!IsCommandLineBatchMode())\n            {\n                Execute(HotUpdatePipelineName);\n                return;\n            }\n\n            Debug.Log($\"BuildPipeline.RunHotUpdatePipeline (batch, all steps): '{HotUpdatePipelineName}'\");\n            BeginBatchCli(HotUpdatePipelineName, selectedOnly: false);\n        }","newText":"        /// <summary>\n        /// 无参入口，供 bat：<c>-executeMethod YYZY.BuildPipeline.BuildPipeline.RunHotUpdatePipeline</c>。\n        /// 执行名为 <see cref=\"HotUpdatePipelineName\"/> 的流水线中<strong>仅勾选的步骤</strong>。\n        /// </summary>\n        public static void RunHotUpdatePipeline()\n        {\n            if (!IsCommandLineBatchMode())\n            {\n                Execute(HotUpdatePipelineName);\n                return;\n            }\n\n            Debug.Log($\"BuildPipeline.RunHotUpdatePipeline (batch, selected only): '{HotUpdatePipelineName}'\");\n            BeginBatchCli(HotUpdatePipelineName, selectedOnly: true);\n        }"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input"