{"type":"message","id":"ca26c8c6","parentId":"2cd02b33","timestamp":"2026-05-27T06:12:58.919Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The hot update pipeline succeeded! Let me summarize for the master.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"## ✅ 热更流水线成功！\n\n流水线全部跑通了，开发群也已经 @兵王 通知了。\n\n**本次改动总结：**\n- 改了 `BuildPipeline.cs` 的 `RunHotUpdatePipeline()`，`selectedOnly: false` → `true`\n- 之前每一次都因为 GitPull 步骤强制执行失败，现在只跑勾选的步骤\n- 以后手动 git 更新主工程 + 子模块，流水线只管编译和上传 CDN"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":2515,"output":114,"cacheRead":78976,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":81605,"cost":{"input":0.00035210000000000005,"output":0.00003192,"cacheRead":0.002211328,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002595348}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779862376376,"responseId":"2b790248-6b79-4686-b09b-cb2013166a67"}}
