{"type":"message","id":"7c43e185","parentId":"32497b09","timestamp":"2026-05-27T06:52:02.095Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me update:\n1. `memory/2026-05-27.md` - today's log\n2. Update TOOLS.md with the code change info\n3. Update MEMORY.md with the key change","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_gz50VbbBDPILrXPEqA6l7758","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 2026-05-27 日志\n\n## 热更流水线修复\n\n### 问题\n流水线内 GitPull 步骤即使取消勾选，在 batch mode 下仍被执行。\n原因是 `RunHotUpdatePipeline()` 硬编码了 `selectedOnly: false`，导致所有有效步骤全部执行。\n\n### 修复\n改了 `E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv\\Assets\\Editor\\BuildPipeline\\BuildPipeline.cs`：\n- `RunHotUpdatePipeline()` 内 `selectedOnly: false` → `selectedOnly: true`\n- 注释和日志也同步更新\n\n现在命令行跑流水线只执行勾选的步骤。\n\n### 流程变更\n- 以前：主仓库 git pull，子模块由流水线内部 Git 拉新处理\n- 现在：主仓库 + 所有子模块全部手动 git pull/checkout 更新，流水线不再负责拉新\n- 需要检查子模块 detached HEAD 状态，切到正确分支再 pull\n\n### 执行结果\n共跑了 4 次流水线：\n1. ❌ 子模块 detached HEAD -> git更新失败\n2. ❌ 修好子模块但 GitPull 仍执行 -> git更新失败\n3. ❌ 取消勾选 GitPull 但 batch mode 无视勾选 -> git更新失败\n4. ✅ selectedOnly=true 修复后成功\n\n## 更新测试包通知\n补丁已推送到 CDN，版本 1.0.41（Android），开发群 @兵王 已通知。\n","path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\memory\\2026-05-27.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":48,"output":458,"cacheRead":82304,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":82810,"cost":{"input":0.00000672,"output":0.00012824,"cacheRead":0.002304512,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002439472}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779864715412,"responseId":"8207b9a4-b11d-4f87-bd77-be3e0e39504d"}}
