{"type":"message","id":"82bba58f","parentId":"9df63bd3","timestamp":"2026-05-27T06:52:06.347Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now update TOOLS.md - I need to add the code change info to the hot update section, and also update the git handling steps.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_xRo5hxgaNzRRhA5RUIFR1791","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\TOOLS.md","edits":[{"oldText":"**注意:**\n- 首次使用需在 Unity Editor 中打开 BuildPipeline 窗口配置好 \"热更\" 流水线的各步骤参数\n- 运行需要管理员权限（Unity 许可证校验）\n- 完整的日志会输出到 `BuildPipeline_RunHotUpdate.log`\n- **默认使用增量构建模式**（不清理 Bundles 缓存），速度更快。仅当资源丢失或异常时才需手动全量构建","newText":"**注意:**\n- 首次使用需在 Unity Editor 中打开 BuildPipeline 窗口配置好 \"热更\" 流水线的各步骤参数\n- 运行需要管理员权限（Unity 许可证校验）\n- 完整的日志会输出到 `BuildPipeline_RunHotUpdate.log`\n- **默认使用增量构建模式**（不清理 Bundles 缓存），速度更快。仅当资源丢失或异常时才需手动全量构建\n- **2026-05-27 重要修复：** 改了 `BuildPipeline.cs` 的 `RunHotUpdatePipeline()`，`selectedOnly: false` → `true`。之前 batch mode 无视勾选强制跑所有步骤，导致已取消勾选的 GitPull 仍被执行"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":166,"output":371,"cacheRead":82688,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":83225,"cost":{"input":0.00002324,"output":0.00010388,"cacheRead":0.002315264,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002442384}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779864722107,"responseId":"72429f1d-e85c-4b06-abb1-49ab3be89865"}}
