{"type":"message","id":"6df10848","parentId":"d97612b0","timestamp":"2026-05-27T07:53:30.121Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, Unity process killed. Now spawn a sub-agent to handle the full pipeline:\n1. git pull main repo\n2. Check and fix submodules\n3. Run the hot update pipeline\n4. Check results\n5. Notify","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_EC7bJLnLaiGX6MV9kAnd1448","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"label":"hotupdate-client-v5","mode":"run","context":"isolated","task":"# 热更流水线（GitPull 已修复版）\n\n## 前置\n- Unity 进程已关闭 ✅\n- GitPull 已取消勾选 ✅\n- selectedOnly=true 已修复 ✅\n\n## 步骤\n\n### 1. git 手动更新\n```powershell\ncd E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\ngit pull\n```\n\n### 2. 检查并修复子模块 detached HEAD\n```powershell\ncd E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\n# 获取所有子模块状态并检查 detached HEAD\ngit submodule foreach 'git symbolic-ref -q HEAD || echo \"DETACHED:$sm_path\"'\n```\n对 detached HEAD 的子模块，找到正确分支并 checkout + pull。\n\n根据 .gitmodules，子模块分支配置：\n- DidaFramework → Customize_YYZY\n- Server(battle1v1) → YYZY_1V1_V1.0_WeekVersion_0430\n- GordianConfig → 无指定分支（pinned commit，保持 detached）\n- SoloConfig → 无指定分支（pinned commit，保持 detached）\n- Proto → 无指定分支（pinned commit，保持 detached）\n\n如果 Server 子模块 detached，动作用：`git checkout YYZY_1V1_V1.0_WeekVersion_0430 && git pull`\n\n### 3. 运行热更 BAT\n```\nE:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv\\RunBuildPipelineHotUpdate.bat\n```\n\n### 4. 检查编译结果\n```powershell\nSelect-String -Path 'E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv\\BuildPipeline_RunHotUpdate.log' -Pattern 'error CS\\d+:|git更新失败|Build completed with'\n```\n\n### 5. 通知\n**成功 → 开发群 @兵王：**\n```powershell\ncd C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\nnode scripts/feishu_send_group.mjs oc_59afc01122ec0cd04ca4d8c5103c7a77 hotupdate-ok\n```\n\n**失败 → 私聊通知主人，不发群消息。**\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":68,"output":623,"cacheRead":85504,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens